{"tid":539710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"村屋動物園：檢26隻瀕危7隻受保護　由漁護暫養","createTime":"2018-01-24T20:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T20:17:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d31755c267fc8521a867635f6cfdb7fefc4388b3","tid":539710,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T20:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180124/photo/bkn-20180124194235634-0124_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180124201425\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180124%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180124194235634-0124_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180124201425&h=bbfd09b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倉鴞。（<span style=\"color: red;\">梁國雄</span>攝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180124/photo/bkn-20180124194235634-0124_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180124201425\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180124%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180124194235634-0124_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180124201425&h=0f07f53e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑似豹貓。（<span style=\"color: red;\">梁國雄</span>攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180124/photo/bkn-20180124194235634-0124_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180124201425\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180124%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180124194235634-0124_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180124201425&h=8e229019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貓頭鷹。（<span style=\"color: red;\">梁國雄</span>攝）<br />\n<br />\n漁護署發言人表示，昨日(23日)在八鄉兩個處所發現一批動物，當中有26隻屬於《瀕危野生動植物種國際貿易公約》（《公約》）而懷疑非法管有的列明物種，包括<br />\n當中被列入附錄I的物種有懶猴、黑池龜、娃娃魚及七線巨鯉，被列入附錄II的有鳳頭鷹、麻鷹、灰林鴞、褐林鴞及倉鴞，另有數種動物有待確定，包括水獺、豹貓及巨蜥等。<br />\n<br />\n署方亦發現7隻懷疑受保護的野生動物，包括2隻果子狸、3隻紅頰獴及2隻赤腹松鼠。根據《野生動物保護條例》（第170章），任何人除按照特別許可證行事外，不得管有受保護的野生動物。受保護的野生動物是指《野生動物保護條例》的附表2所指明的任何本地野生動物。任何人如違反以上條例，一經定罪，最高可被判罰款10萬元及監禁1年。 <br />\n<br />\n行動中檢走的動物分別於該署的動物管理中心、瀕危物種資源中心及本地動物救援機構暫養，有合適的設施及人手以及專業的知識去照顧這批動物，個案將由警方作跟進調查。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另根據署方資料，昨日行動中所搜查及檢獲動物的2個處所並未領有動物售賣商牌照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180124/bkn-20180124194235634-0124_00822_001.html?refer=fn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180124%2Fbkn-20180124194235634-0124_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dfn2&d=H94%2BgzYnyCrPm1IqZrKhghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3fa3beea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180124/bkn-20180124194235634-0124_00822_001.html?refer=fn2</a>"},{"pid":"d547d8a382c4b3d368f812e3040e39d95e601c9e","tid":539710,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T23:33:33.000Z","msg":"似係野味，用嚟食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a13c26ff5d9bb8cac71badaf635416876ed9f23","tid":539710,"uid":23416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T23:42:53.000Z","msg":"第一隻野個樣好戅鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e868d9d3af5b630a1a6027ec5e1a7c63c5a6efc0","tid":539710,"uid":3775,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7a13c26ff5d9bb8cac71badaf635416876ed9f23","tid":539710,"uid":23416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T23:42:53.000Z","msg":"第一隻野個樣好戅鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T23:44:07.000Z","msg":"唔好咁講自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83287d673ce11ad19652e3c571599d3cf10c4f3d","tid":539710,"uid":68141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T23:46:12.000Z","msg":"豹貓鴛鴦眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cc79d956c95aea2722bdbe6c566e0e96dc15be","tid":539710,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83287d673ce11ad196